---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lang = 'en' as const;
---

<Layout title="Rules & Regulations">
  <div class="pt-24 pb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Rules & Regulations — Stellplatz Petřkovice u Lurdy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-text">
      <p class="text-text-light italic">Parking for motorhomes and caravans</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">1. General rules</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light">
        <li>The stellplatz is intended exclusively for motorhomes and caravans.</li>
        <li>Upon arrival, guests must register and fill out an accommodation card.</li>
        <li>Maximum stay is 3 nights unless otherwise agreed.</li>
        <li>Quiet hours are from 10:00 PM to 7:00 AM.</li>
        <li>Guests are required to keep their pitch and common areas clean and tidy.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">2. Arrival and departure</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light">
        <li>Check-in: from 2:00 PM.</li>
        <li>Check-out: by 12:00 PM (noon).</li>
        <li>Please leave your pitch in its original condition upon departure.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">3. Services and amenities</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light">
        <li>230V electricity — connect as instructed by the operator.</li>
        <li>Fresh water — available at the designated point.</li>
        <li>Grey water — dispose at the marked location.</li>
        <li>Black water (chemical toilet) — dispose at the marked location.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">4. Payment</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light">
        <li>Payment is due on arrival or as agreed with the operator.</li>
        <li>Current pricing is available on the website and at the stellplatz entrance.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">5. Safety</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light">
        <li>Open fires are only permitted in designated areas.</li>
        <li>Pets are welcome but must be kept under control by their owner.</li>
        <li>The operator is not liable for damage to guests' property.</li>
        <li>In case of breakdown or emergency, please contact the operator.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">6. Operator contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light">
        Phone: <a href="tel:+420000000000" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">+420 000 000 000</a><br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@petrkovickelurdy.cz" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">info@petrkovickelurdy.cz</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <a href="/en/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors">&larr; Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
